Package: lite-nas
Version: 0.1.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: Oleksiy Bondar <bondaroleksiyandroyovich@gmail.com>
Pre-Depends: debconf (>= 1.5.0)
Depends: zfsutils-linux, nats-server, openssl, systemd
Recommends: aide, clamav, ufw, usbguard
Description: LiteNAS bootstrap and host profile package
 Applies the LiteNAS host profile, deploys managed configuration, provisions
 common LiteNAS identities, and installs bundled LiteNAS service and app binaries.
